Q_DESC:
A class teacher wants to find the grade for the respective total marks  obtained by the students.Help him by writing a program to find out the grade for the marks obtained.
Input:
Input marks as an integer.
Output:
Display the respective grade for the marks obtained.
Constraint:
((mark=75) (mark=100)) GRADE A
((mark=60) (mark75)) GRADE B
((mark=50) (mark60)) GRADE C
else FAIL
